post_summaries.description: The image is a festive New Year's greeting in Spanish, "Feliz Año," set against a black background adorned with golden decorations. The lettering is stylized with flourishes and highlights, giving it a three-dimensional effect. Golden ornaments hang from the top, and there are also golden floral designs and firework-like bursts scattered around the text. The overall aesthetic is elegant and celebratory.
The image is a "Feliz Navidad" (Merry Christmas) greeting card with Christmas ornaments, pine branches, and confetti.

The image is a post celebrating International LGBT Pride Day. The text in the image includes words like "Amor" (Love), "Respeto" (Respect), "Igualdad" (Equality), "Orgullo" (Pride), "Lucha" (Fight), and "Derechos" (Rights) in the colors of the rainbow flag.
The image shows a light box that reads "HAPPY PRIDE MONTH" in front of a rainbow flag.

The image is a New Year's greeting card with "2024" displayed prominently in gold, along with fireworks and a city skyline silhouette. The caption wishes a happy 2024 to family, friends, and acquaintances, with wishes for health, love, and prosperity.

The image is an Instagram post by victormercadopvdm wishing "Felices Fiestas" (Happy Holidays) to his family, friends, contacts, and acquaintances. It features the text "¡Felices Fiestas!" inside a stylized Christmas ornament.
